-- UK's Chesnara to buy Waard Group, CEO to step down
-- By Richa Naidu in Bengaluru
-- Wed Dec 03, 2014 02:25AM EST
-- None



Dec 3 (Reuters) - Chesnara Plc <CSN.L>, an insurance-focused takeover specialist, said it would buy Waard Group for 67.8 million euros ($83.9 million) and that Chief Executive Graham Kettleborough would step down after Dec. 31.

